[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 7.64,
    "text": "Hi, we're agents Cletus and Spinetti, U.S. Secret Service."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.64,
    "endTime": 14.36,
    "text": "We're here doing a pre-event security sweep where Trump will be having his rally in two weeks here in Pennsylvania."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.36,
    "endTime": 15.36,
    "text": "That's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.36,
    "endTime": 19.24,
    "text": "The security of the president and his life are our only objectives."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.24,
    "endTime": 26.839999999999996,
    "text": "We're going to need this tree line taken down to offer more of a clear line of sight from that area directly to the podium."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.08,
    "endTime": 33.839999999999996,
    "text": "Hey Spinetti, what do you think of this building 150 yards from the podium with a ladder affixed to the back of it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.84,
    "endTime": 35.639,
    "text": "150 yards?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.639,
    "endTime": 40.0,
    "text": "We should consider that outside of the 500-yard perimeter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.0,
    "endTime": 41.0,
    "text": "Copy that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.0,
    "endTime": 45.919,
    "text": "Hey, it looks like this roof has a pretty clear line of sight going straight to the podium."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.919,
    "endTime": 47.958999999999996,
    "text": "You think we should station someone up there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.959,
    "endTime": 48.959,
    "text": "Negative."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.959,
    "endTime": 51.68000000000001,
    "text": "The director said the roof is way too sloped."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.68,
    "endTime": 56.72,
    "text": "She considers it too dangerous for agents whose job it is to take a bullet for the president."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.759,
    "endTime": 57.759,
    "text": "What is that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.759,
    "endTime": 58.759,
    "text": "About a 10-degree angle?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.759,
    "endTime": 60.36,
    "text": "It's actually 5 degrees."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.36,
    "endTime": 61.88,
    "text": "So no agents up there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.88,
    "endTime": 65.72,
    "text": "Instead, she wants them up there on that roof with a 30-degree slope."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.72,
    "endTime": 66.72,
    "text": "Roger that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.72,
    "endTime": 70.48,
    "text": "So any agents stationed on the ground over by the ladder of that building?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.48,
    "endTime": 75.76,
    "text": "No, that building 150 yards from the stage is outside of our 500-yard perimeter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.76,
    "endTime": 77.27900000000001,
    "text": "Ah, big numbers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.279,
    "endTime": 78.279,
    "text": "Copy that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.279,
    "endTime": 82.59899999999999,
    "text": "Now in the unlikely event that there is a disruption, what's going to be our exit strategy for the president?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.839,
    "endTime": 87.599,
    "text": "I, you know, I think we'll just kind of feel it out in a moment."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.599,
    "endTime": 88.599,
    "text": "See what's up then."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.599,
    "endTime": 90.199,
    "text": "Oh, go with the flow?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.199,
    "endTime": 91.199,
    "text": "Kind of like a Daoism?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.199,
    "endTime": 92.199,
    "text": "Exactly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.199,
    "endTime": 95.44,
    "text": "You know, kind of rise to the occasion kind of thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.44,
    "endTime": 97.67999999999999,
    "text": "All right, we're all secure here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.68,
    "endTime": 98.68,
    "text": "Good work today, Spinetti."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.68,
    "endTime": 99.68,
    "text": "Oh, thank you, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.68,
    "endTime": 107.68,
    "text": "Ah, it's a good day for a rally."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.68,
    "endTime": 111.959,
    "text": "Cletus, we've got reports of a man with a rifle near Building 3."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.32,
    "endTime": 113.32,
    "text": "Copy that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.32,
    "endTime": 114.32,
    "text": "I'll get eyes on him in about 30 minutes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.32,
    "endTime": 124.44,
    "text": "Cletus, yeah, we're now being informed by 37 eyewitnesses that the man is climbing atop"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.44,
    "endTime": 129.399,
    "text": "Building 3 with a device shaped similarly to a rifle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.399,
    "endTime": 131.199,
    "text": "What is, is he hunting?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.199,
    "endTime": 132.199,
    "text": "Probably."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.199,
    "endTime": 134.119,
    "text": "There's a lot of whitetail in the area."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.119,
    "endTime": 137.36,
    "text": "Well, you know, venison's pretty good if you know how to cook it right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.36,
    "endTime": 138.36,
    "text": "Sure is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.36,
    "endTime": 139.36,
    "text": "Yeah, butter, butter, some red wine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.36,
    "endTime": 140.36,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.36,
    "endTime": 141.36,
    "text": "Well, just report back to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.759,
    "endTime": 142.759,
    "text": "Let me know if he gets a deer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.759,
    "endTime": 145.759,
    "text": "Get down, get down, get down, get down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.759,
    "endTime": 147.759,
    "text": "Shot, shot's fired."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.759,
    "endTime": 149.759,
    "text": "Oh, did he get one?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.759,
    "endTime": 151.759,
    "text": "Uh, apparently he was shooting at the stage."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.759,
    "endTime": 152.759,
    "text": "Shh, shh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.759,
    "endTime": 153.759,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.759,
    "endTime": 154.759,
    "text": "There's deer on the stage?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.759,
    "endTime": 158.759,
    "text": "Uh, they're saying he shot Trump."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.759,
    "endTime": 160.759,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.759,
    "endTime": 161.759,
    "text": "That doesn't sound right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.759,
    "endTime": 162.759,
    "text": "Let me check Twitter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.759,
    "endTime": 164.759,
    "text": "Oh my God!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.759,
    "endTime": 165.759,
    "text": "He shot Trump!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.759,
    "endTime": 167.759,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.759,
    "endTime": 168.759,
    "text": "Oh my God, oh my God, oh my God."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.759,
    "endTime": 169.759,
    "text": "Yeah, he got him!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.16,
    "endTime": 173.16,
    "text": "Oh God, oh God, oh God, this is bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.16,
    "endTime": 175.16,
    "text": "Dude, just calm down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.16,
    "endTime": 176.16,
    "text": "What do we do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.16,
    "endTime": 177.16,
    "text": "I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.16,
    "endTime": 178.16,
    "text": "I thought you knew what to do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.16,
    "endTime": 180.16,
    "text": "Holy shit, dude."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.16,
    "endTime": 181.16,
    "text": "We could have been killed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.16,
    "endTime": 182.16,
    "text": "I know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.16,
    "endTime": 185.16,
    "text": "Okay, we gotta get to the stage."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.16,
    "endTime": 186.16,
    "text": "Come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.16,
    "endTime": 187.16,
    "text": "Oh, Jesus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.16,
    "endTime": 188.16,
    "text": "House."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.16,
    "endTime": 191.16,
    "text": "Okay, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.16,
    "endTime": 194.16,
    "text": "Okay, I think it's, I think it's loaded."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.16,
    "endTime": 195.16,
    "text": "Come on!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.16,
    "endTime": 197.16,
    "text": "What do we do when we get to the stage?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.16,
    "endTime": 199.16,
    "text": "Take cover behind the president."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.559,
    "endTime": 200.559,
    "text": "He's got a big body."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.559,
    "endTime": 201.559,
    "text": "Copy that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.559,
    "endTime": 202.559,
    "text": "Now what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.559,
    "endTime": 203.559,
    "text": "Get your head down, idiot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.559,
    "endTime": 205.559,
    "text": "There might be more shots fired."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.559,
    "endTime": 207.559,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.559,
    "endTime": 212.559,
    "text": "Sir, Mr. Trump, do you watch out for your blood?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.559,
    "endTime": 213.559,
    "text": "It's getting all over my suit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.559,
    "endTime": 216.559,
    "text": "I don't even see any deer up here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.559,
    "endTime": 219.559,
    "text": "He might have been trying to shoot the president."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.559,
    "endTime": 221.559,
    "text": "Really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.559,
    "endTime": 222.559,
    "text": "Maybe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.559,
    "endTime": 223.559,
    "text": "Okay, they're moving him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.559,
    "endTime": 224.559,
    "text": "We're losing our cover."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.559,
    "endTime": 225.559,
    "text": "Let's get to the car."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.559,
    "endTime": 226.559,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.559,
    "endTime": 228.559,
    "text": "Where's the car?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.96,
    "endTime": 229.96,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.96,
    "endTime": 230.96,
    "text": "I don't have the keys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.96,
    "endTime": 231.96,
    "text": "I think someone else parked it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.96,
    "endTime": 233.96,
    "text": "Why is there no one here to help us?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.96,
    "endTime": 234.96,
    "text": "I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.96,
    "endTime": 237.96,
    "text": "Like, they got the president in the car."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.96,
    "endTime": 238.96,
    "text": "Let's get there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.96,
    "endTime": 240.96,
    "text": "Secure the perimeter of the vehicle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.96,
    "endTime": 241.96,
    "text": "Copy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.96,
    "endTime": 242.96,
    "text": "Copy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.96,
    "endTime": 250.96,
    "text": "How do you know if you're having a panic attack?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.959,
    "endTime": 259.959,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.959,
    "endTime": 261.959,
    "text": "I think we're good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.959,
    "endTime": 262.959,
    "text": "Okay, good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.959,
    "endTime": 266.959,
    "text": "I think we're at the wrong car."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.959,
    "endTime": 269.959,
    "text": "Yeah, no one's in there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.959,
    "endTime": 270.959,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.959,
    "endTime": 271.959,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.959,
    "endTime": 273.959,
    "text": "Looks like this just isn't the right car."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.959,
    "endTime": 277.959,
    "text": "When we were running up, I could have sworn it was a giant black SUV."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.959,
    "endTime": 279.959,
    "text": "Oh, I could have sworn it was."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.959,
    "endTime": 280.959,
    "text": "F**k."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.359,
    "endTime": 293.359,
    "text": "We at Trump Secret Service Detail that works for the Biden administration consider the security of today's rally to be a great success."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.359,
    "endTime": 294.359,
    "text": "That's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.359,
    "endTime": 297.359,
    "text": "Let's not forget that only one president was shot today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.359,
    "endTime": 298.359,
    "text": "And he only got shot once."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.359,
    "endTime": 301.359,
    "text": "And it was in the ear, and he has two of those."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.359,
    "endTime": 302.359,
    "text": "Plus, he lived."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.359,
    "endTime": 307.359,
    "text": "And we neutralized the would-be assassin in under 60 minutes from the first sighting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.359,
    "endTime": 308.359,
    "text": "That's pretty good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.359,
    "endTime": 309.359,
    "text": "That's fantastic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.76,
    "endTime": 313.76,
    "text": "Especially when you consider that that is less time than your average episode of 60 minutes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 313.76,
    "endTime": 328.76,
    "text": "We'd also like to thank the director of the U.S. Secret Service for her initiatives in hiring a diverse team of agents with a diverse range of abilities, good and bad, when it comes to protecting a former president from being murdered in public."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.76,
    "endTime": 340.15999999999997,
    "text": "Yeah, as part of the mentally handicapped community, there's not many other organizations that are willing to hire people like us for jobs that involve having guns and keeping presidents alive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.16,
    "endTime": 342.16,
    "text": "So, for our work today, you're welcome."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.16,
    "endTime": 344.16,
    "text": "You're in good hands, America."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.16,
    "endTime": 350.16,
    "text": "Now, if you'll excuse us, we've got to go eat mayonnaise out of jars because we think it's peanut butter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.16,
    "endTime": 351.16,
    "text": "Mm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.16,
    "endTime": 352.16,
    "text": "You have any more of those paint chips?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.16,
    "endTime": 353.16,
    "text": "Got a few."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356.16,
    "endTime": 357.16,
    "text": "That's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.16,
    "endTime": 361.16,
    "text": "The security of the president and keeping him alive are our only objectives."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 361.16,
    "endTime": 362.16,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.16,
    "endTime": 364.16,
    "text": "How is that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.16,
    "endTime": 365.16,
    "text": "Hello?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 365.16,
    "endTime": 366.16,
    "text": "It's Jack."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.16,
    "endTime": 367.16,
    "text": "Hey, Jack."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 367.16,
    "endTime": 368.16,
    "text": "Oh, tell him I said hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 368.559,
    "endTime": 369.559,
    "text": "Hey, Stinson says hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 370.559,
    "endTime": 371.559,
    "text": "Yeah, I got time to talk."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 371.559,
    "endTime": 372.559,
    "text": "It doesn't matter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.559,
    "endTime": 373.559,
    "text": "You saw what happened recently."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 373.559,
    "endTime": 374.559,
    "text": "We all did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.559,
    "endTime": 379.559,
    "text": "So now, more than ever, protecting the security of your family is more important than ever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 379.559,
    "endTime": 382.559,
    "text": "And that's exactly what real men and real women do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 382.559,
    "endTime": 389.559,
    "text": "And part of protecting your family is being responsible for the security of your family's important documents and passwords."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.559,
    "endTime": 391.559,
    "text": "But how are you going to do that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 391.559,
    "endTime": 397.559,
    "text": "Because people like you and I have awakened to the fact that you can't trust normal cloud storage service companies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 397.959,
    "endTime": 403.959,
    "text": "Bunker is a secure cloud storage, password manager, surveillance-free messaging app."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.959,
    "endTime": 408.959,
    "text": "Did you know passwords continue to be the leading vector of online vulnerability?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 408.959,
    "endTime": 413.959,
    "text": "But Bunker takes care of that, and their encrypted cloud storage eliminates other attack vectors."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 413.959,
    "endTime": 419.959,
    "text": "And think about the recent breach of all AT&T customers' call logs and text messages."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.959,
    "endTime": 420.959,
    "text": "That affected me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 420.959,
    "endTime": 422.959,
    "text": "That doesn't happen with Bunker."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 423.359,
    "endTime": 429.359,
    "text": "We all have a million passwords nowadays, and we need the peace of mind to know our passwords are stored securely."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 429.359,
    "endTime": 433.359,
    "text": "And I love Bunker's free, no-surveillance private messaging."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 433.359,
    "endTime": 435.359,
    "text": "Oh, but I use Signal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 435.359,
    "endTime": 440.359,
    "text": "Well, you might not want to anymore when you find out Tucker Carlson and RFK Jr."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.359,
    "endTime": 443.359,
    "text": "reported their Signal accounts were spied on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 443.359,
    "endTime": 448.359,
    "text": "For the love of freedom and the security of your family, protect what's most important to your family."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 448.76,
    "endTime": 452.76,
    "text": "Go to the App Store or Play Store now and download Bunker."
  },
  {
